Hello friends. I added a table of strong MA/EMA levels. Zones of long-term key support and resistance levels have been added to the chart. These levels will be very useful in the next 12 months in search of a bottom and the start of a global uptrend.I added spot markets to the hourly chart (they show key strong levels better due to the deep history of the chart). Now you can compare the price of the Binance spot and futures market + see the price of futures on other major exchanges. I would be grateful for likes on YouTube👍🏻Good luck everyone and have a nice weekend!
